==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skilled
<hw>Skilled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having familiar
knowledge united with readiness and dexterity in its application;
familiarly acquainted with; expert; skillful; -- often followed by
<xex>in</xex>; <as>as, a person <ex>skilled</ex> in drawing or
geometry</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Skillet</ent>⟦br⟧
